I am a Second-Year grad student at the University of Michigan, in the [Quantitative Finance and Risk Management](https://lsa.umich.edu/math/graduates/quantitative-finance.html) program. I did my undergraduate work in Applied Mathematics at Xiamen University. My hobbies are skiing and traveling.
